9-0.query:
SELECT MIN(an.name) AS alternative_name, MIN(chn.name) AS character_name, MIN(t.title) AS movie
FROM sampled_aka_name_4 AS an,
 sampled_char_name_4 AS chn,
 sampled_cast_info_4 AS ci,
 sampled_company_name_4 AS cn,
 sampled_movie_companies_4 AS mc,
 sampled_name_4 AS n,
 sampled_role_type_4 AS rt,
 sampled_title_4 AS t
WHERE ci.movie_id = t.id
 AND t.id = mc.movie_id
 AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
 AND mc.company_id = cn.id
 AND ci.role_id = rt.id
 AND n.id = ci.person_id
 AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
 AND an.person_id = n.id
 AND an.person_id = ci.person_id
AND ci.note IN ('@param0')
AND cn.country_code = '@param1'
AND mc.note IS NOT NULL 
AND (mc.note LIKE '@param2' OR mc.note LIKE '@param3')
AND n.gender = '@param4'
AND n.name LIKE '@param5'
AND rt.role = '@param6'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN @param7 AND @param8;
